 {"id":"br-r37-c1-sd104","title":"parity: write_graphml_xml/lxml missed infer_numeric_types kwarg","description":"fnx.write_graphml has infer_numeric_types but the two named-variant aliases write_graphml_xml and write_graphml_lxml omitted it from their signatures, so write_graphml_xml(G, path, infer_numeric_types=True) raised TypeError. nx exposes it on all three. Aligned both wrappers to forward through to write_graphml. 5 parity tests freeze the contract.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-26T03:51:01.274232337Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T03:51:43.837990653Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T03:51:43.836131344Z","close_reason":"Fixed in commit 0c2b828. write_graphml_xml/lxml now expose infer_numeric_types in slot #5 matching nx, and forward all kwargs through to write_graphml. 5 parity tests freeze the contract.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-sgjko","title":"parity: time-respecting isomorphism matchers missing","description":"NetworkX exposes TimeRespectingGraphMatcher(G1, G2, temporal_attribute_name, delta) and TimeRespectingDiGraphMatcher(G1, G2, temporal_attribute_name, delta). FrankenNetworkX does not export these classes, leaving temporal VF2 matcher API unavailable. Add wrappers that convert FrankenNetworkX graph objects via _networkx_graph_for_parity and delegate to NetworkX, plus parity tests for signatures and isomorphism mappings on temporal graph/digraph paths.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"cod-networkx","created_at":"2026-04-25T09:31:58.717555427Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-25T09:35:34.565138940Z","closed_at":"2026-04-25T09:35:34.563236879Z","close_reason":"Completed in 739ccaa","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-uuo38","title":"parity: classes.filters hide_*/show_*/no_filter wrappers (11 fns)","description":"networkx.classes.filters exposes 11 filter factory functions used to construct subgraph views: hide_nodes(nodes), hide_edges(edges), hide_diedges(edges), hide_multiedges(edges), hide_multidiedges(edges), show_nodes(nodes), show_edges(edges), show_diedges(edges), show_multiedges(edges), show_multidiedges(edges), no_filter(*items). franken_networkx does not surface these. Add Python wrappers in __init__.py exporting at top-level + __all__. Each returns a filter callable used by subgraph_view.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-04-25T22:49:38.907487801Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-25T23:04:39.857592364Z","closed_at":"2026-04-25T23:04:39.855657558Z","close_reason":"Shipped in de44f96: 11 filter factory wrappers (hide_/show_ variants for nodes/edges/diedges/multiedges/multidiedges, plus no_filter). Verified including end-to-end subgraph_view(P5, filter_node=hide_nodes([2])) -> [0,1,3,4].","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
+{"id":"br-r37-c1-v0ryp","title":"parity: maybe_regular_expander missing create_using/max_tries kwargs","description":"fnx.maybe_regular_expander(n, d, seed=None) lacked nx's keyword-only create_using=None and max_tries=100. Drop-in callers passing either kwarg hit TypeError. Aligned signature so the alias matches the longer maybe_regular_expander_graph and nx exactly. 5 parity tests freeze the contract.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-26T03:56:47.373364568Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T03:56:47.373364568Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-vw7p2","title":"parity: connectivity is_locally_k_edge_connected missing","description":"networkx.algorithms.connectivity.is_locally_k_edge_connected(G, s, t, k) tests local k-edge-connectivity between s and t. Not exposed by franken_networkx. Add Python wrapper delegating to networkx and export at top-level.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-25T11:51:45.929293966Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T03:15:26.852652308Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T03:15:26.850843424Z","close_reason":"Already implemented in fnx — top-level export matches nx.connectivity exactly. Landed tests/python/test_connectivity_parity_extras.py (commit 3765516) with 37 cases freezing the contract.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-wjv9o","title":"parity: tree.branchings + tree.mst edge iterators (5 fns)","description":"Five tree-related utilities from networkx.algorithms.tree not surfaced. Branchings: branching_weight(G, attr=weight, default=1), minimal_branching(G, *, attr=weight, default=1, preserve_attrs=False, partition=None). MST edge iterators: boruvka_mst_edges, kruskal_mst_edges, prim_mst_edges (all signature G, minimum, weight=weight, keys=True, data=True, ignore_nan=False, partition optional). These give users access to the underlying MST/branching algorithm primitives. Add Python wrappers in __init__.py exporting at top-level + __all__.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-04-25T22:24:47.743148985Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-25T22:39:41.161615863Z","closed_at":"2026-04-25T22:39:41.159730985Z","close_reason":"Shipped in 7cca063: branching_weight + minimal_branching + boruvka/kruskal/prim mst_edges iterators. All 5 verified on weighted K5 (MSTs match nx exactly) and 3-node DiGraph (branching weight + edge count match).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-wpydo","title":"parity: community leiden_communities + leiden_partitions missing","description":"networkx.algorithms.community.leiden_communities(G, ...) and leiden_partitions(G, ...) (Leiden community detection algorithm) not exposed by franken_networkx. Add Python wrappers delegating to nx.algorithms.community via _call_networkx_community_for_parity. Export both at top-level and include in __all__ under community detection section.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-25T12:06:41.073069778Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-25T13:05:29.824008425Z","closed_at":"2026-04-25T13:05:29.822140820Z","close_reason":"Shipped in 4eb0d6d: leiden_communities/partitions wrappers; mirrors nx NotImplementedError parity","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
